From: Benjamin Drung <benjamin.drung@canonical.com>
Date: Thu, 5 Mar 2026 19:19:29 +0100
Subject: test: switch from isc-dhcp-server to dnsmasq

isc-dhcp-server is no longer activly maintained and has been removed
from Debian testing.

Use dnsmasq as DHCP server instead.

Fixes: https://github.com/dracut-ng/dracut-ng/issues/1451
Forwarded: https://github.com/dracut-ng/dracut-ng/pull/2271
